Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.62,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Rain on a sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:35.00,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Out here in outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:41.16,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}In a tangled web, many vows are said in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:47.99,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Crossing the veil of night, beyond the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.83,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Can future science become supernatural?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:00.49,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fscx95}And in a blink of an eye you and I, cast adrift in this quiet expanse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:06.66,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Nothing but consciousness, we're terrified and alone, far from home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.80,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}And as our bodies dissolve into dust
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.21,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Our life's purpose is over and done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:17.16,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Now countless particles and pixels journey on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:20.83,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Travel on toward tomorrow's universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:28.13,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Here in the solar dance we spin, setting to pre-delete, meta-reference
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:34.99,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Understanding is beyond our reach forever, we're seeking intervention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:40.66,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Space and time, putting it all on the line—ENIAC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:47.99,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fscx92\fad(250,250)}Time's arrow isn't hitting its chosen target, lost in chaos, failing from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:53.63,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}As billions of processes align, parallelism
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.73,op tl,,0,0,0,,{\iclip(0,0,0,0)\t(4003,4003,\iclip(854,967,1067,1200))\t(4035,4035,\iclip(641,967,1281,1200)\t(4070,4070,\iclip(427,967,1497,1200)\fad(250,250)}Should we never learn to rewrite our future history—
